description: [``botocore``] This release enhances the SearchProfiles API by providing functionality to search for profiles using multiple keys and logical operators.
[``botocore``] This release adds a new parameter "Parameters" in the DataLakeSettings.
[``botocore``] Updating the API docs data type: NetworkEthereumAttributes, and the operations DeleteNode, and CreateNode to also include the supported Goerli network.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for restoring an RDS Multi-AZ DB cluster snapshot to a Single-AZ deployment or a Multi-AZ DB instance deployment.
[``botocore``] Added 2 new document related operations, DeleteDocumentVersion and RestoreDocumentVersions.
[``botocore``] This release enhances GetServiceGraph API to support new type of edge to represent links between SQS and Lambda in event-driven applications.
